ory and beauty - serving for big Hollywood productions such as Star Wars and Games Of Throne as Kings Landing. \n\n- TIME TRAVEL TO 1667 -\n\nGAME FEATURES\n\u2022    14 historically accurate 360 scenes\n\u2022    Voice-over narration\n\u2022    Video documentaries", "short_description": "Dubrovnik Anno 1667 is a historical overview of an old Croatian city Dubrovnik. Once an independent state Dubrovnik was a maritime powerhouse standing up to Venice. Experience Dubrovnik as it was before a devastating earthquake that happened in 1667. Today Dubrovnik is known worldwide for its history and beauty - serving for big Hollywood productions such as Star Wars and Games Of Throne as Kings Landing. "}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://mediaupprodukcija.wixsite.com/mediaup/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "MediaUp", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://mediaupprodukcija.wixsite.com/mediaup/dubrovnik-1667-anno", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["EXPERIENCE_360_NON_GAME", "CASUAL", "NARRATIVE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["GEAR_VR_CONTROLLER"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "518866932789339"}, "review_messages": ["", "", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974622_396487261595134_4387279445664348464_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=JRVnA_OEeVQQ7kNvgFSXYA6&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=Ay_P8kQ-QiyiRv2dwAcHBdb&oh=00_AYBdvTdUXSvlDrqP2GcAOjZkVZhjVR1o